Anastrozole
PRONUNCIATION (an AS troe zole)

BRAND NAME(S): Arimidex

WHAT IS THIS DRUG USED FOR? It is used to treat breast cancer in women after change of life.;  It may be given to you for other reasons. Talk with the doctor.

